# ğŸ§  ShellSteward â€” Your AI-Powered Shell Companion

ShellSteward is a smart command-line assistant that translates natural language prompts into shell commands using semantic search. Whether you're navigating directories, inspecting files, or debugging your environment, ShellSteward helps you do it faster and smarter.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ” Natural language to shell command retrieval  
- ğŸ§  Semantic search using SentenceTransformers + FAISS  
- ğŸ› ï¸ Cross-shell support (bash, zsh, cmd, PowerShell)  
- ğŸ§ª Doctor command to verify setup and dependencies  
- ğŸ“‹ History tracking and clipboard support  
- âš™ï¸ Configurable shell preferences and onboarding  

